"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1927675-Olympics-Andy-Murray-retirement-tennis-news\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Andy Murraydoesn't have a clear idea of what he wants to do when the curtain closes on his illustrious tennis career after his involvement at the2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 161, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But, with the distraction of professional tennis in the rear mirror, the British sporting icon has hinted that he is aiming to progress his golf career.\", \"from\": 162, \"to\": 314, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 235, \"end\": 242, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9994775495614135, \"rank\": 0.00031074389911890904, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray will savour his swansong on the Roland Garros court this summer as he prepares to represent Team GB in the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 316, \"to\": 442, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 316, \"end\": 322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7155844117960107e-17, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 355, \"end\": 368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"score\": 0.9999006915592348, \"rank\": 9.931716922415465e-05, \"text\": \"Roland Garros\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\"}, {\"begin\": 415, \"end\": 422, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9987411525754638, \"rank\": 0.0012017103928738193, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 37-year-old's Olympic prowess speaks for itself, winning back-to-back gold medals in the men's singles at London 2012 and Rio 2016.\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 579, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 623, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 694, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 688, \"end\": 693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996725819, \"rank\": 3.274967442558356e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 799, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 769, \"end\": 781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9999375649689324, \"rank\": 6.243884842619062e-05, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 854, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, an emotional final farewell awaits in the French capital, where he will enter the men's doubles alongside British No.\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 978, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 903, \"end\": 909, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9979512967510762, \"rank\": 0.0019629028203620074, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 967, \"end\": 974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9994775495614135, \"rank\": 0.00031074389911890904, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"3 Dan Evans.\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 991, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 981, \"end\": 990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"score\": 0.9984112046854962, \"rank\": 0.0015913235764383412, \"text\": \"Dan Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But what next?\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1007, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Where will Murray go once his final point plays out - be it for elimination or glory?\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1093, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1019, \"end\": 1025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7155844117960107e-17, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The great man himself could not provide a definitive answer on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1167, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not know exactly what the rest of my life will look like, but I will still stay in touch with the sport,\\\" Murray explained during an interview in the Olympic Village.\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1341, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1281, \"end\": 1287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7155844117960107e-17, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 1325, \"end\": 1340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 7.167533778981697e-13, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not see that ever changing.\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1376, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My love for [tennis] will not go away, so I will definitely see myself staying involved.\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1465, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u200c\\\"Initially, I want to be at home with my family.\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1516, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to spend a lot of time with my kids and my wife, so I will not be on the road much, I know that.\\\"\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1621, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1727, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1758, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Once his ambitions in one sport expire, though, those in another emerge.\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 1855, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray is a keen golfer, and he plans to invest time in improving on the fairway.\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1937, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1856, \"end\": 1862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7155844117960107e-17, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u200cHe continued: \\\"I will play a lot of golf - I want to become a scratch golfer.\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 2017, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have always loved playing golf, but because of the issues with my back, I have not played for five or six years.\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2132, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would also love to be part of the next Olympics in some capacity, but I do not have any clear plans on what it is I am going to do from a work perspective.\\\"\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2293, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He would perhaps struggle to match his standard on the tennis court, but becoming a scratch golfer - a player who shoots par or better on a consistent basis - is no mean feat.\", \"from\": 2295, \"to\": 2470, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not see myself playing any of the invitational things or those sort of events,\\\" Murray added when asked about a potential future tennis return.\", \"from\": 2472, \"to\": 2621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2558, \"end\": 2564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7155844117960107e-17, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2623, \"to\": 2732, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2733, \"to\": 2809, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2842, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  \\\"I expect I will still hit some balls and stuff, but when I play sport, I like to compete - whether that's in cards, golf or whatever.\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 3001, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to be competitive.\", \"from\": 3002, \"to\": 3027, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not want to just have 